Equitorial Trust Investors Approve Sterling Merger, ThisDay Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-09-07T08:20:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/equitorial-trust-investors-approve-sterling-merger-thisday-says.html
Equitorial Trust Bank Plc’s
shareholders and board approved the lender’s acquisition by
 Sterling Bank (STERLNBA)  Plc of  Nigeria ,  ThisDay  reported, citing Managing
Director Gbolahan Folayan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 